 and transportation sectors as well as in progressively responsible positions in europe and north america in product and manufacturing engineering sales product line management acquisition integration and general management he received both a bachelors degree and a masters degree in electrical engineering from the ohio state university• korn ferry a global people and organizational advisory firm named dhritiman chakrabarti senior client partner of the korn ferry hay group previously he was the regional leader for the rewards talent and communications business for asia pacific in a leading global advisory firm chakrabarti is a graduate of delhi university and the institute of management technology in india• fitbit inc a connected health and fitness market leader announced samir kapoor has been promoted from vp of engineering to senior vp of device engineering kapoor most recently was with qualcomm kapoor is a graduate of iit bombay washington state university the university of notre dame and the wharton school of business at the university of pennsylvania • acr alpine capital research llc a valueoriented asset management firm named neel shah as a portfolio manager prior to joining acr shah was at bluemountain capital management and oaktree capital management• familyowned bacardi limited one of the world’s largest privately held spirits companies announced that mahesh madhavan a year bacardi veteran will succeed michael j dolan as ceo in april  madhavan was previously a member of the company’s global leadership team and regional president of asia middle east and africa during the transition madhavan will serve as regional president of europe for much of  during his tenure at bacardi madhavan has held leading roles within various emerging markets including managing director of india thailand and the philippines and south asia and southeast asia he has also led the company’s emerging market council• voisin consulting life sciences named dr gopalan narayanan vp of disruptive biologics narayanan was previously at the uk medicines and healthcare products regulatory agency for  years four years leading the biologicals unit • farient advisors an independent corporate governance and executive compensation advisory firm named zanvi patel as a partner patel was previously at etrade financial in varying roles of leadership as well as a consultant at mclagan and johnson associates she holds a mba and a bs from the nyu stern school of business• ofg bancorp named ganesh kumar formerly executive vp and cfo as senior executive vp and coo kumar will also be in charge of ofg’s strategic business development and expansion endeavors kumar  who has a doctorate in management from case western reserve university in ohio joined ofg in  as an evp and has been the cfo since  × post a comment as emoticons smile beam wink sad cool innocent rolleyes whistling lol huh tongue love sleeping yawn unsure angry blink crying ohmy scared sleep sneaky tonguesmile thumbdown thumbup censored happybirthday ban spam offtopic batman ninja pirate alien comment text cancel post comment × report cancel report abuse × watch this discussion stop watching this discussion get an email notification whenever someone contributes to the discussion notifications from this discussion will be disabled cancel start watching stop watching  comments welcome to the discussion log in keep it clean please avoid obscene vulgar lewd racist or sexuallyoriented language please turn off your caps lock dont threaten threats of harming another person will not be tolerated be truthful dont knowingly lie about anyone or anything be nice no racism sexism or any sort of ism that is degrading to another person be proactive use the report link on each comment to let us know of abusive posts share with us wed love to hear eyewitness accounts the history behind an article post a comment watch this discussion stop watching this discussion submit your news were always interested in hearing about news in our